  hpfrei/body-anatomy-3d-viewer
  https://github.com/hpfrei/body-anatomy-3d-viewer
  Licensed under CC BY-SA 4.0.

This project (Muscle Atlas 3D — interactive exercise anatomy & shoulder triage)
builds on the above and is distributed under the same CC BY-SA 4.0 license.

